   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国、是受格拉克斯·杜加奇严密统{00}制的国家……",
   "zh_hex": "15d4b5e8f8a102e7b6e8c8e824e7c2e7d5e7c804e8cbe854e904eaa1e9bde92900e8dee7b4a1e7df090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66ee",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、只要打倒杜加奇、木星帝国就会瓦{00}解！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef32ef2ae7f5e848e8cbe854e90402d4b5e8f8a1e7c5e7e2e99f00e89d060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x672e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！那么、立刻开始行动！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97e7b7e7bd02e86be91fe7fae908efd6ef30ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6743",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各舰、准备出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d402e87ae877afe7cc060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6756",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "准备一就绪、我们就向木星帝国军、发起{00}决战！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e87ae877efb6e7c5efee02efcce7bbe7c5efc1efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e002e870e84700e8abef28ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67b2",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67d4",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、贝尔纳黛特？是睡不着吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf05e7b6ebdee7b5e86de802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6806",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在想些事情……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7e6e8a4efb8e88b09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6839",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……贝尔纳黛特？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x685e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父亲……",
   "zh_hex": "15e888e89409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6866",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我觉得、父亲或许早已不在了",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8aee80a02e888e894e905e8a7e963ef3ae7b5ef29e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6883",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、现在向木星军下令的、是父亲的复{00}制人格！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e82fef29efc1efa9ef69e7e0ef4de94ee7b402e7b6e888e894e7b4e9ee00e8deefb2e824ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68a2",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "否则做不出那种事……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9bbea87e81ce7b5efbee7b7e7d1efb80909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68d5",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝尔纳黛特……",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68f9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、托比亚！所以……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e7f4e825e7d606e7fbe7f30909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x690e",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以快阻止他！求你阻止他吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3e85fe8efe869e80cef97e93ae7b8e8efe869e80ce7d0ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6920",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别再让父亲的执念、{00}做出更过分的事了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e80be7f9e888e894e7b4e9fcea270200e81cafe952ef36cde7b4a9e7ba060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6954",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没事、贝尔纳黛特",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8efb802e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6967",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我一定……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefb6e8670909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x698f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f66",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？是拉·凯拉姆！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef9705e7b6e7c2ef4be95fe7c2e823ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f79",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！可恶的隆德·贝尔队！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7c4e7dee7b4ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f89",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "知道逃不掉、就索性豁出去了吗！！{00}全舰、转入攻击态势！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85ae82ae8c2e7b5e9d302e7c5e93ce951eba5afe7ebe7bae802060600bbe7d402e9c2e8919ee7cce994e8fd0606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8fd2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……中计了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef4eea55e7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9001",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
